  "prompt": "Where can I get very professional fire inspection service in Sydney?",
  "response": "In Sydney, several reputable companies offer professional fire inspection services. Here are a few options you can consider:\n\n1. **Fire Safety Australia** - They provide a full range of fire safety services, including inspections, compliance assessments, and certification.\n\n2. **Williams Fire & Safety** - Specializes in fire protection services, including inspections, maintenance, and equipment supply.\n\n3. **JTM Fire Safety** - Offers comprehensive fire safety services, including fire inspections, compliance services, and training.\n\n4. **SAAA Fire Safety** - Provides fire safety and inspection services, ensuring compliance with Australian standards and regulations.\n\n5. **Firecom** - They offer fire safety consulting, inspections, and design services tailored to various facilities.\n\nMake sure to check their credentials, reviews, and qualifications to ensure you choose a service that meets your specific needs. It's also a good idea to reach out to multiple companies for quotes and to discuss your requirements.",
